[SHORT DESC]
Adds 1 EV to Special Attack. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]

<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Adds 1 Special Attack EV to the target Pok√©mon per use, until it has 255 Special Attack EVs. Also increases the Pokemon's happiness.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>This item can be found at Driftveil Drawbridge and Marvelous Bridge by walking in the shaded circles that occasionally appear on the bridges. Found in both Black and White versions.</p>